This topic describes how to configure Pivotal Cloud Foundry (PCF) Ops Manager on Azure Germany.

First, you must complete the steps in [Prepare Azure](./azure-prepare-env.html) and [Deploying BOSH and Ops Manager to Azure Manually](./azure-om-deploy.html).

Then, in the BOSH Director tile, select **Azure German Cloud** from the **Azure Environment** dropdown.

For more information about configuring Azure, see [Azure Config Page](azure-om-config.html) in the _Configuring Ops Manager on Azure_ topic.